  "title": "Clinic Nurse ( Fresh Graduate welcome)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li><strong>Office Hours (Alternate Saturdays Off)</strong></li><li><strong>Central Area</strong></li><li><strong>Attractive Staff Incentives</strong></li></ul><p><br />We are representing our client, a <strong>Urology Specialist Clinic</strong>, in seeking a <strong>Clinic Nurse</strong> with the following requirements:<br /><br /><strong>Job Scope</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Provide general nursing care and assist doctors in clinic consultations and procedures.Support and manage daily clinic operations.</li><li>Perform counter and administrative duties when required</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Diploma in Nursing and registered with the <strong>Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</strong>.</li><li>A strong team player who is detail-oriented and service-driven.</li><li>Possesses good interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Willing to learn, proactive, and carries a positive <em>can-do</em> attitude.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>How to Apply</strong><br /><br />Interested applicants, please send your detailed resume to <a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/clinic-nurse-salohealth-management-cbbfca6c9937c4c37ba39e43aca9989d/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">recruitment@salo.sg</a> or WhatsApp <strong>88681573</strong>.<br /><br />We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Applicants who may not meet all requirements will still be considered based on overall merit and may be contacted for other suitable opportunities<br /><br /><strong>SALOHealth Management</strong><br /><strong>EA Licence No.: 24C2535</strong></p>",
